Articles.Content:
I was trying out a new mod I had made, a single piece rocket. The model loaded fine but at launch it did not fill with electrical charge a right click show that it had 0.00 electrical charge even though it was supposed to have 5. The light at the bottom remained purple so I ended the flight. I added the launch stabilizers thinking that they would charge it up. This time at launch it still had no power and the light remained purple for about 20 seconds, at this point in time the game crashed and provided me with the following.

https://www.dropbox.com/s/jbvjbfuhanpih4t/2013-06-20_001828.zip

EDIT:

Windows 7

Super big fancy computer

Mods: Yes, mine so probably buggy

I think the issue lies in having too many part modules on one part. . . maybe?
You'd probably do better to check with other modders in the appropriate forum sections, and include the actual part.cfg so they can see if you missed something.
